data.name: Cmd_UpdateIsRequired
data.value:
Vi ber om ursäkt för eventuella besvär, men det är nödvändigt att installera varje ny uppdatering. Dessa uppdateringar kan innehålla kvalitetsförbättringar och vissa kan även inkludera kritiska säkerhetsfixar.
Om du av någon anledning inte kan uppdatera Stella Mod via launchern, avinstallera den nuvarande versionen och installera den nya från den officiella webbplatsen.

data.name: Default_ItLooksLikeYouAreLaunchingTheLauncherForTheFirstTime
data.value:
Hello! It looks like you're launching the launcher for the first time. Please take a moment to review the terms of use and guidelines for this modification in the official documentation to avoid any potential issues.
The software is continuously supported by the developer thanks to Stella Plus subscribers. Subscription revenues cover the costs of fiber-optic internet and electricity bills. The API server is hosted in a private home in Poland, ensuring that the local administrator is the sole owner of the data. This guarantees the security of your device's hardware data, which is processed according to the highest privacy standards. Stella Mod Launcher prioritizes privacy and security. No analytical data is sent to the server without your consent.
Stella Mod is safe software, so you don't need to worry about anything. Just remember not to use cheats. If you need help, join our Discord server or send an email to contact@sefinek.net. Have fun!
